This paper deals with statistical analysis and natural language processing techniques to extract trending topics from Bangla newspapers. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves techniques for clustering and visualization, which are commonly used in Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Social Networks (cs.SI). The use of machine learning algorithms for data analysis and pattern recognition also suggests the sub-categories of Deep Learning (cs.DL) and Software Engineering (cs.SD).
